The paper deals with bibliometric analysis and data collection, which are common topics in the fields of digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and databases (cs.DB). The use of seed+expand methodology for identifying author publications also involves network analysis and graph algorithms, which are relevant to the sub-category of complex systems (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
